## Tailwind configuration snippet

```js
// tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  content: ["./**/*.html"],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        'ink-900': '#0C0F14',
        'charcoal-800': '#111315',
        'ethics-green': '#6CE0C3',
        'climate-blue': '#58A4FF',
        'sand-100': '#F4F0EC',
        'accent-warm': '#FFC857',
        'muted-400': '#9AA3A8'
      },
      fontFamily: {
        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto'],
        mono: ['JetBrains Mono', 'monospace']
      }
    }
  }
}
```

